{
  "texts": [
    "Here, we'll delve into these models in more detail to provide a clear understanding of their methods.",
    "The DeepDDS model employs two different types of GNNs: GAT and GCN.",
    "These GNNs are assessed to extract features from the molecular graphs of drugs.",
    "The genomic characteristics of cancer cells are encoded using a MLP.",
    "These resulting embeddings are combined to create the ultimate feature representation for each combination of drug and cell line."
  ]
}